{"tid":194431,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"大師 Sebastião Salgado 給年輕攝影師的建議","createTime":"2017-04-10T03:12:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T13:49:59.000Z","uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7143289e63da81b5d2ea44329fde69638411f0c4","tid":194431,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T03:12:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.thephoblographer.com/2016/09/28/sebastiao-salgados-advice-young-photographers-today/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thephoblographer.com%2F2016%2F09%2F28%2Fsebastiao-salgados-advice-young-photographers-today%2F&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWRy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=e56ef13c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.thephoblographer.com/2016/09/28/sebastiao-salgados-advice-young-photographers-today/</a><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;If you&rsquo;re young and have the time, go and study. Study anthropology, sociology, economy, geopolitics. Study so that you&rsquo;re actually able to understand what you&rsquo;re photographing. What you can photograph and what you should photograph.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"4602fc46c739c16eaed230107002b3c58cb86ebf","tid":194431,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T03:16:04.000Z","msg":"其實都適用於班大叔，就係少無咩學識先至有咁多糖水相"},{"pid":"0eadf5ad434d7bba8026f504f5b8b3ba9fdfe0b5","tid":194431,"uid":3811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T03:17:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實都適用於班大叔，就係少無咩學識先至有咁多糖水相</blockquote><br />\n咁始終要有人影糖水相我地先有J打， 又唔好抺殺佢地既貢獻"},{"pid":"87ba02fa651ef54691060e2d9bfb43e84e7bcfb5","tid":194431,"uid":27991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T03:18:21.000Z","msg":"認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇見到打龍阿叔真係嘔心"},{"pid":"a48fa69c7c549767662b64133412b32b351f3231","tid":194431,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T03:33:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"14f1dfb1dfc72e0e3c6